      },
      "writtenOn": "2014-09-12T17:42:51Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "OK. I understand. I still think this sort of logic deserves to be implemented in interface/class/method similar to what I\u0027ve out-lined above and shouldn\u0027t be repeated for every single http resource method that we are implementing.",
      "revId": "abaf9e2b2c41a167b79388aa3c4f482f81ae7887",
